data.description: Discover the allure of this beautifully updated main-level living home, offering breathtaking 270-degree views of Thumb Butte and Granite Mountain. Beyond its double front doors, the panorama of Granite Mountain unfolds through a stunning 4-panel sliding glass door in the living room, creating a picturesque backdrop that is nothing short of mesmerizing. Step into the living room, where a vaulted ceiling, a gas fireplace with a rock surround, and tile floors with a wood-floor inlay set the stage for elegance and comfort. Recent updates to the kitchen include a striking ''white glass'' refrigerator and dishwasher, complementing the shaker-style cabinets, granite counters, & a convenient walk-in pantry. The adjacent dining area becomes the ideal spot to witness the sunset over Granite Mountai
